  "description": "<b>最近有消息称苹果计划在加州Palo Alto的斯坦福购物中心建造一个规模更大更加现代化的新零售店，以此来抗衡微软实体店的威胁。</b>据悉该店设计方案早在2011年就以完成，零售店拥有视觉上在漂移的屋顶，行人可以更大的视角看到零售店，另外一个巨大的石头墙，将会分割零售店的前侧和后侧。目前该零售店已经开始施工，下面是目前记者从施工现场外围拍摄下来的照片。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d61b42a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241392.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%8E%A2%E7%8F%AD%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%9B%B4%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241392.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%8E%A2%E7%8F%AD%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%9B%B4%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241392.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%8E%A2%E7%8F%AD%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%9B%B4%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241392.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%8E%A2%E7%8F%AD%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%9B%B4%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.f